{{Quote|''An immersive action-adventure with over 8 hours of gameplay. Take on intense bullet hell combat‚ punch and fight robots‚ and tackle platforming challenges all powered by time control abilities. Solve intricate puzzles and face epic boss battles that test your skills. Save your progress to play at your own pace‚ and unlock thrilling New Game+ modes for even more action. Favorite this world and join the fight!}}

'''Bullet Time Agent''' is a PC-only [[:Category:Game worlds|game world]] created by Lakuza, and was released on November 21st, 2024. Limited versions of Bullet Time Agent are available on Android, but are divided up by stage.

